         ruby-gnome2
Description: Software designed to help authors to write their books
 Bookwrite is a software designed to help authors to write their books. 
 It provides a full screen editor without any nuisances, that allow 
 authors to focus completely on their texts. It also provides a few other 
 features, that will be added for each new version.
